lse,"excerpt":"Abu al-\u2018Aliyah reported: They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the words we just heard you say?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThey are words that the Angel Gabriel, upon him be peace, taught me as an expiation for gatherings: Glory be to You, O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15342,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/dua-gathering-idle-talk\/","url_meta":{"origin":15344,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication after idle talk in gathering","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sits in a gathering and indulges in idle talk, then let him say before leaving that gathering, 'Glory be to You, O Allah, and Your praises. I bear witness there is no God but You,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19731,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/08\/10\/repentance-supplication-glory-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15344,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Repentance: Glory to Allah, I seek your forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 10, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said these words often before he passed away, \u201cGlory be to Allah and with His praise. I seek Your forgiveness and I repent to You.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I see you have said these words\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32848,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/praise-allah-who-fed-me\/","url_meta":{"origin":15344,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Praise be to Allah who fed me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever eats a meal and says, \u2018All praise is due to Allah, who fed me this from his provision without any capability or strength on my part,\u2019 his previous minor sins will be forgiven.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34638,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/angels-praise-gathering-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":15344,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Angels praise gatherings to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people gather to remember Allah, only desiring by that His countenance, except that it will be announced for them in the heavens: Stand forgiven! Your bad deeds have been replaced with good deeds!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u06